<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tiripuvaṉaccakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrīrājarāja</hi> tevaṟkku yāṇṭu pa<unclear>ti</unclear>
<lb n="2"/>nañcāvatu nāyaṉār tirukkāḷattiuṭaiya nāyaṉārkku <hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>cikulacāḷukki 
<lb n="3"/>tirukkāḷattitevanāṉa yātavarāyar <unclear>mākkaḷakatti</unclear>l peri kuvaḷai<unclear>k</unclear>oṭ<unclear>ṭu</unclear> malaiyil
<lb n="4"/>Irukkuṅ kaṭṭitevaṉ <unclear>pi</unclear>lāvanāṉa veṇāṭuṭaiyāṉ tirununtāviḷakku Oṉṟuk
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ku viṭṭa cāvā muvāp perāṭu toṇṇūṟṟuāṟum polikiṭāy Oṉṟum po
<lb n="6" break="no"/>limottai Oṉṟum Ikkoyil tiruviḷakku Iṭaiyaril<note n="256-1">The record is left unfinished.</note>
</p>

